# —— 不影响 App 运行 / 可本地再生成的内容 ——
# 克隆后执行: cd app && flutter pub get && flutter run

# Flutter SDK（体积大，请自行安装）
SDK/

# IDE / 编辑器
.idea/
**/.idea/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Flutter / Dart 构建与缓存（运行前会自动再生成）
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.packages
**/.pub-cache/
**/.pub/
**/coverage/
**/doc/api/

# 各桌面平台 ephemeral 生成目录
**/ephemeral/
**/windows/flutter/ephemeral/
**/linux/flutter/ephemeral/
**/macos/Flutter/ephemeral/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
**/ios/Flutter/Flutter.podspec

# Android 本地/构建相关（密钥与本机路径）
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/local.properties
**/android/**/.cxx/
**/android/app/debug/
**/android/app/profile/
**/android/app/release/
**/android/**/key.properties
**/*.keystore
**/*.jks

# 混淆 / 符号化产物
**/app.*.symbols
**/app.*.map.json

# 日志与系统垃圾
*.log
*.pyc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.history/
migrate_working_dir/

# 一次性维护脚本 / 仅本地说明（不参与编译运行）
**/_check_docs.py
**/PLEASE_DELETE.txt
